  1â†’//! Batch analyze: send Analyze requests for discovered files and aggregate into a function registry.
  2â†’//!
  3â†’//! The [`FunctionRegistry`] is a unified collection of all functions found across
  4â†’//! all source files. Each [`FunctionEntry`] records the file path, function metadata,
  5â†’//! and branch count. This registry is the input to call graph construction.
  6â†’
  7â†’use std::collections::HashMap;
  8â†’use std::path::{Path, PathBuf};
  9â†’
